<sect1 id="jbigkit" xreflabel="JBIG-KIT-&jbigkit-version;">
  <?dbhtml filename="jbigkit.html"?>

  <title>JBIG-KIT-&jbigkit-version;</title>

  <indexterm zone="jbigkit">
    <primary sortas="a-JBIG-KIT">JBIG-KIT</primary>
  </indexterm>

  <sect2 role="package">
    <title>Introduction</title>

    <para>
      <application>JBIG-KIT</application> is a software implementation of the
      JBIG1 data compression standard (ITU-T T.82), which was designed for
      bi-level high-resolution image data such as scanned documents.
    </para>

