  <sect2 role="installation">
    <title>Installation</title>

    <para>
      Install <application>JBIG-KIT</application> by running the following
      commands:
    </para>

<screen><userinput>patch -Np1 -i ../jbigkit-2.0-fixes-1.patch &amp;&amp;
make</userinput></screen>

    <para>
      Use this sed to disable installing the static library:
    </para>

<screen><userinput>sed -i 's|libjbig/.libs/\*.a||' Makefile</userinput></screen>

    <para>
      Now, as the <systemitem class="username">root</systemitem> user:
    </para>

<screen role="root"><userinput>make install</userinput></screen>

  </sect2>

